attachments.text:
STRANGERS is a new anthology of animated shorts presented by LATE NIGHT WORK CLUB.
Featuring new work by Sean Buckelew, Nicolas Menard, Kirsten Lepore, Alex Grigg, Jeanette Bonds, Loup Blaster, and Caleb Wood. 
Coming November 28th. For more info follow at @L8NightWorkClub on twitter dot com.
